## Interface: 20505
## Title: LibCodex-1.0-Factions
## Notes: Bundled seed data for LibCodex-1.0 / Factions (TBC Anniversary flavor). LoadOnDemand: LibCodex-1.0 auto-loads this on first :Get() miss against the Factions module. Per-module split keeps the core lib's bytecode pool tiny and lets consumers pay only for modules they query.
## Author: ChronicTinkerer
## Version: 8
## LoadOnDemand: 1
## Dependencies: LibCodex-1.0
## X-Curse-Project-ID: 1532131
## X-License: MIT

# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# Factions catalog for the TBC Anniversary flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against Factions.

Data_TBC\Factions.lua
